<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Ahoy.cf - @ViewBag.StrID</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.5.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans+KR:300,400">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/styles.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <section class="text-center" style="background: #1C313A;height: 300px;">
        <div style="height: 100px;"></div>
        <div class="container" style="padding-right: 60px;padding-left: 60px;">
            <div class="shadow p-2 mb-5 bg-white rounded">
                <div class="input-group mb-0 mt-0" style="height: 38px;margin-top: 1px;">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control mb-0 mt-0 shadow-none" id="txtUrl" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;" readonly value="@ViewBag.Shorted">
                    <div class="input-group-append mb-0 mt-0"><button class="btn btn-dark mb-0 mt-0" type="submit" style="height: 38px;margin-top: 10px;font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;font-weight: 100;" onclick="CopyText();">복사</button></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="container" style="margin-top: -30px;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col" style="background: #ffffff;box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgb(173,173,173);border-radius: 5px;padding: 20px;">
                <h2 class="mb-3 mt-1" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;">링크 정보</h2>
                <p class="mb-0" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-info-circle">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 0 8 1a7 7 0 0 0 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"></path>
                        <path d="M8.93 6.588l-2.29.287-.082.38.45.083c.294.07.352.176.288.469l-.738 3.468c-.194.897.105 1.319.808 1.319.545 0 1.178-.252 1.465-.598l.088-.416c-.2.176-.492.246-.686.246-.275 0-.375-.193-.304-.533L8.93 6.588z"></path>
                        <circle cx="8" cy="4.5" r="1"></circle>
                    </svg>&nbsp;아이디:&nbsp;@ViewBag.ID
                </p>
                <p class="mt-0 mb-0" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-eye">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16 8s-3-5.5-8-5.5S0 8 0 8s3 5.5 8 5.5S16 8 16 8zM1.173 8a13.134 13.134 0 0 0 1.66 2.043C4.12 11.332 5.88 12.5 8 12.5c2.12 0 3.879-1.168 5.168-2.457A13.134 13.134 0 0 0 14.828 8a13.133 13.133 0 0 0-1.66-2.043C11.879 4.668 10.119 3.5 8 3.5c-2.12 0-3.879 1.168-5.168 2.457A13.133 13.133 0 0 0 1.172 8z"></path>
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 5.5a2.5 2.5 0 1 0 0 5 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5zM4.5 8a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 7 0 3.5 3.5 0 0 1-7 0z"></path>
                    </svg>&nbsp;조회수:&nbsp;@ViewBag.View
                </p>
                <p class="mt-0 mb-0" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-calendar">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.5 0a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V1h8V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 1 0V1h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5zM1 4v10a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h12a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V4H1z"></path>
                    </svg>&nbsp;등록일:&nbsp;@ViewBag.Date
                </p>
                <p class="mt-0 mb-0" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-lock-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M2.5 9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h7a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9z" />
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 4a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 7 0v3h-1V4a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-5 0v3h-1V4z" />
                    </svg>&nbsp;비밀번호 사용여부:&nbsp;@ViewBag.UsePassword
                </p>
                <p class="mt-0" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-link-45deg">
                        <path d="M4.715 6.542L3.343 7.914a3 3 0 1 0 4.243 4.243l1.828-1.829A3 3 0 0 0 8.586 5.5L8 6.086a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.154.199 2 2 0 0 1 .861 3.337L6.88 11.45a2 2 0 1 1-2.83-2.83l.793-.792a4.018 4.018 0 0 1-.128-1.287z"></path>
                        <path d="M6.586 4.672A3 3 0 0 0 7.414 9.5l.775-.776a2 2 0 0 1-.896-3.346L9.12 3.55a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.793.792c.112.42.155.855.128 1.287l1.372-1.372a3 3 0 0 0-4.243-4.243L6.586 4.672z"></path>
                    </svg>&nbsp;짧아진 URL:&nbsp;@ViewBag.Shorted
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center w-100 mb-0" style="position : fixed; bottom:0;">Made with&nbsp;♥&nbsp;by Kate Lin<br></p>
    <script>
        function CopyText() {
            var copyText = document.getElementById("txtUrl");
            copyText.select();
            copyText.setSelectionRange(0, 99999);
            document.execCommand("copy");
        }
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.5.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>